{"tid":1887130,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問及派錢 張建宗：相信財政司司長聽到大家聲音","createTime":"2020-02-19T10:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T15:03:24.000Z","uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2258ac66b7075c98664d599e22dec2d4cb09d0","tid":1887130,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:29:39.000Z","msg":"立法會就應對新型冠狀病毒疫情措施展開急切口頭質詢。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會黃國健形容，現時人心惶惶，詢問政府會否開倉派錢，要求每人最少一萬元。議員毛孟靜形容，特首林鄭月娥是「攬炒之母」，有如放火後扮救火，質疑政府不全面封關為照顧北京的「玻璃心」。<br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗說，明白市民面對前所未見的困難，疫情對經濟影相當大，政府下星期三將發表預算案，相信財政司司長聽到大家聲音。他希望議員盡快通過抗疫基金撥款，支援不同項目以共渡時艱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509425-20200219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509425-20200219.htm&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5HlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=6e0d8fe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509425-20200219.htm&h=f0a21efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509425-20200219.htm</a>"},{"pid":"422538aef1612a8139e24f8e1a7ca6d395b58e0d","tid":1887130,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:30:25.000Z","msg":"咁樣跣囤地波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4845290bf6fce42646bf6bc2da085006e36ea2b0","tid":1887130,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"有機喎"},{"pid":"571cbeb6927425b6d3843b6ef3fc43bb1f2d9088","tid":1887130,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473d540c567a948ffa96a469e49ff8802d12908a","tid":1887130,"uid":94828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"422538aef1612a8139e24f8e1a7ca6d395b58e0d","tid":1887130,"uid"